Sentencas: An integrated fuel cell system based on tubular fuel cells is examined.
Titulo: Integrated fuel cell system with tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The system relies on free convection to pass air and spent gas through the system by using a chimney.
Titulo: Integrated fuel cell system with tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Thus, an expensive air supply mechanism is not required.
Titulo: Integrated fuel cell system with tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is shown that the use of free convection up to a power generating scale of around 2 kW is feasible.
Titulo: Integrated fuel cell system with tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Factors determining the dimensions of the heat exchanging system are studied.
Titulo: Integrated fuel cell system with tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A complete system capable of generating 2 kW of electricity, running on natural gas and ambient air, is anticipated to have a diameter of approximately 300 mm and a height of 1700 mm.
Titulo: Integrated fuel cell system with tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Including the chimney a total height of 5 m was found.
